#: ../../geovista/docs/src/overview.rst:96
msgid "Static and interactive plot integration within `Jupyter`_ ecosystem"
msgstr "`Jupyter`_ エコシステム内での静的およびインタラクティブなプロットの統合"

#: ../../geovista/docs/src/overview.rst:100
msgid ":fa:`battery-quarter` Development Status"
msgstr ""

#: ../../geovista/docs/src/overview.rst:102
msgid ""
"It's still early days for ``geovista``, but we're already excited about the "
"potential and promise that it might offer to the Earth Science community."
msgstr "``geovista`` はまだ日が浅いですが、地球科学コミュニティに提供できる可能性と将来性にすでに興奮しています。"

#: ../../geovista/docs/src/overview.rst:105
msgid ""
"Our primary focus at the moment is to provide a stable API and core set of "
